1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 18=

3
00:00:56,439 --> 00:00:57,119
Sorry.

4
00:00:57,679 --> 00:01:00,119
The subscriber you dialed
is currently unavailable.

5
00:01:00,600 --> 00:01:01,560
Please try again later.

6
00:01:02,280 --> 00:01:03,159
It was a diversion.

7
00:01:03,560 --> 00:01:05,400
After realizing it wasn't Ji Xuan,

8
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,480
he turned back.

9
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,359
What?

10
00:01:07,879 --> 00:01:09,879
So, you mean...

11
00:01:10,040 --> 00:01:11,560
He wanted to kidnap Xuan?

12
00:01:11,840 --> 00:01:12,359
Yes.

13
00:01:16,319 --> 00:01:18,719
(Song Zhaoli,
come alone with the money.)

14
00:01:19,159 --> 00:01:20,879
(I'll only wait for half an hour.)

15
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,239
Song!

16
00:01:25,439 --> 00:01:27,239
Wait, wait! It's not untied yet!

17
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,079
Go, go, go! He can't drive!

18
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,640
Song!

19
00:01:58,519 --> 00:01:59,040
Xiao Jin.

20
00:02:04,799 --> 00:02:06,480
You know it's me just by the outline?

21
00:02:06,879 --> 00:02:09,000
Honestly, I'm kind of touched.

22
00:02:17,759 --> 00:02:19,159
I spent years taking care of you.

23
00:02:19,360 --> 00:02:20,719
Five million from Song Zhaoli

24
00:02:20,960 --> 00:02:22,240
isn't too much, right?

25
00:02:22,759 --> 00:02:24,000
Why drag him in?

26
00:02:25,360 --> 00:02:26,599
I kidnapped you.

27
00:02:26,840 --> 00:02:28,800
Who else would be
threatened besides him?

28
00:02:32,280 --> 00:02:33,000
What's so funny?

29
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:34,400
You're pathetic.

30
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:37,280
You want to be strong,
but you lack the ability.

31
00:02:37,719 --> 00:02:39,960
So you sleep with your boss's wife
and threaten your ex.

32
00:02:40,719 --> 00:02:43,280
You're the biggest loser in the world.

33
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:45,840
I wasn't going to do this.

34
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:47,800
But you just had to push your luck!

35
00:02:52,039 --> 00:02:53,000
What are you doing?

36
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,120
Xiao Jin!

37
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:01,960
Ji Xuan, I've had enough
of your bad temper.

38
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:04,479
Wasn't that what you loved?
That I never backed down?

39
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,719
That was before!

40
00:03:05,960 --> 00:03:07,520
Back then, it was cute.

41
00:03:07,759 --> 00:03:08,840
But now,

42
00:03:09,919 --> 00:03:11,319
it's just disgusting.

43
00:03:13,080 --> 00:03:15,080
I really don't know
what Song Zhaoli sees in you.

44
00:03:15,319 --> 00:03:16,779
I've told you many times.

45
00:03:17,216 --> 00:03:18,479
He's just my boss.

46
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:20,360
Save that lie for yourself.

47
00:03:20,520 --> 00:03:21,680
Look at him once,

48
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:23,439
and I know exactly what he's thinking.

49
00:03:50,600 --> 00:03:52,760
♪I saw my love, my love♪

50
00:03:52,928 --> 00:03:54,760
♪Meet you♪

51
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:57,760
♪Fire to my heart♪

52
00:03:57,792 --> 00:04:01,400
♪Lonely, lonely, in my life♪

53
00:04:02,048 --> 00:04:04,480
♪Calling, where are you♪

54
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:08,520
♪I wish I could kiss on you♪

55
00:04:09,520 --> 00:04:11,760
♪I'll wait for you♪

56
00:04:12,280 --> 00:04:15,560
♪Something lost in my soul♪

57
00:04:18,496 --> 00:04:23,360
♪Love, love, I fell in love, are you♪

58
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:30,720
♪Love, I see the sky. It's you♪

59
00:04:32,960 --> 00:04:37,760
♪Love, love, I found you. Can you see♪

60
00:04:38,360 --> 00:04:39,880
♪You see me♪

61
00:04:40,128 --> 00:04:46,040
♪I couldn't leave you
in my life. It's you♪

62
00:04:47,584 --> 00:04:48,640
♪My life♪

63
00:04:49,344 --> 00:04:52,280
♪My heart, this love, it's you♪

64
00:04:54,752 --> 00:04:56,040
♪My life♪

65
00:04:56,576 --> 00:04:59,648
♪My heart, this love for you♪

66
00:05:02,639 --> 00:05:03,439
Xiao Jin!

67
00:05:10,399 --> 00:05:11,240
I'm sorry, Xuan.

68
00:05:12,399 --> 00:05:13,040
I'm late.

69
00:05:19,040 --> 00:05:19,879
Look out!

70
00:05:26,759 --> 00:05:27,439
Trash!

71
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,399
You low life!

72
00:05:28,480 --> 00:05:29,839
- Go to die!
- You loser!

73
00:05:30,040 --> 00:05:31,399
I trusted you so much before.

74
00:05:31,759 --> 00:05:32,680
You let me down.

75
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,720
We called the police.

76
00:05:33,920 --> 00:05:35,120
They'll arrest you.

77
00:05:36,800 --> 00:05:38,480
Stay conscious.

78
00:05:38,639 --> 00:05:40,800
You can't close your eyes. Talk to me.

79
00:05:41,639 --> 00:05:42,319
Xuan.

80
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:45,480
If we can get out of here,

81
00:05:46,759 --> 00:05:48,240
can we be together?

82
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:49,560
Okay.

83
00:05:50,519 --> 00:05:52,240
If we get out safely,

84
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:53,680
we'll be together.

85
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:09,600
Wake up, Song Zhaoli!

86
00:06:09,600 --> 00:06:11,160
Can you hear me? Wake up!

87
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,360
When I got hurt for you at school,

88
00:06:13,360 --> 00:06:15,279
you looked at me
with that same heartache.

89
00:06:15,399 --> 00:06:15,920
Wake up!

90
00:06:15,920 --> 00:06:16,920
- For our life,
- Wake up!

91
00:06:16,920 --> 00:06:19,480
I groveled before Mrs. Wang like a dog.

92
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:23,160
Every time I felt like giving up,

93
00:06:23,160 --> 00:06:25,319
all I could picture
was your face, aching for me.

94
00:06:25,319 --> 00:06:27,160
Shut up! Shut up!

95
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,439
Wake up!

96
00:06:31,552 --> 00:06:33,160
Song Zhaoli, wake up!

97
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:34,199
Stop faking it!

98
00:06:34,199 --> 00:06:35,639
Do you hear me?

99
00:06:36,279 --> 00:06:36,839
Song!

100
00:06:38,208 --> 00:06:38,800
Come on.

101
00:06:38,944 --> 00:06:39,480
Let's go.

102
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:41,720
Be careful.

103
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:44,680
♪My life♪

104
00:06:45,216 --> 00:06:48,840
♪My heart, this love for you♪

105
00:06:52,079 --> 00:06:54,279
I did it all for our happy life.

106
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:57,439
Was I wrong?

107
00:06:59,959 --> 00:07:01,920
I wasn't wrong!

108
00:07:07,800 --> 00:07:08,519
Ji Xuan.

109
00:07:10,519 --> 00:07:13,279
If I wanted to kill you,
they wouldn't have gotten here in time.

110
00:07:22,000 --> 00:07:23,879
Song!

111
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:26,639
Song!

112
00:07:30,079 --> 00:07:30,720
Song!

113
00:07:36,240 --> 00:07:37,920
Song!

114
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:39,160
Song, get up!

115
00:07:44,519 --> 00:07:45,160
No way.

116
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,792
Song Zhaoli.

117
00:07:50,176 --> 00:07:52,120
Aren't you supposed to be all-powerful?

118
00:07:54,240 --> 00:07:55,439
Get up!

119
00:07:56,319 --> 00:07:57,399
Get up!

120
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:00,639
"All-powerful"?

121
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:04,920
Song's just a sucker
who quietly gives everything.

122
00:08:05,879 --> 00:08:07,560
He has PTSD.

123
00:08:08,199 --> 00:08:09,160
He can't drive.

124
00:08:09,639 --> 00:08:11,040
When he heard you were in trouble,

125
00:08:11,439 --> 00:08:13,000
he hit the gas harder than anyone.

126
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,360
To find a kidney donor,

127
00:08:15,680 --> 00:08:17,519
he went and got tested himself.

128
00:08:17,519 --> 00:08:18,480
Ready

129
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,279
to be the backup donor.

130
00:08:21,160 --> 00:08:21,759
Even...

131
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:28,920
Song Zhaoli,

132
00:08:29,720 --> 00:08:31,199
you can't die.

133
00:08:31,759 --> 00:08:34,000
You still don't know
how I feel about you.

134
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:37,639
You don't know my feelings for you.

135
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:39,200
You have no idea

136
00:08:39,744 --> 00:08:41,320
I like you.

137
00:08:41,559 --> 00:08:43,720
Song Zhaoli, get up now!

138
00:08:43,960 --> 00:08:45,039
Get up this instant!

139
00:08:46,320 --> 00:08:47,120
Xuan.

140
00:08:53,039 --> 00:08:53,919
I told you,

141
00:08:54,279 --> 00:08:56,720
pick on me all you want,
but don't mess with Xuan.

142
00:08:56,879 --> 00:08:57,519
Yes.

143
00:08:58,039 --> 00:09:00,559
Ji Xuan is your friend,
but Song is my buddy.

144
00:09:00,759 --> 00:09:02,480
He almost lost his life.

145
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,639
I need to know
if it was worth it for him.

146
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,080
Where's Song Zhaoli?

147
00:09:07,720 --> 00:09:08,360
He's fine.

148
00:09:08,600 --> 00:09:11,120
To avoid affecting the company,
his grandpa

149
00:09:11,240 --> 00:09:12,240
had him treated at home.

150
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:14,679
If you're worried about him,
go see him yourself.

151
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:21,600
It's okay now.

152
00:09:29,879 --> 00:09:31,200
There, there.

153
00:09:37,759 --> 00:09:38,519
It's over.

154
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,279
Everything's fine.

155
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,679
Your relationship with Song Zhaoli

156
00:09:49,919 --> 00:09:52,440
must remain strictly professional.

157
00:09:52,679 --> 00:09:53,879
I'm sorry, Chairman.

158
00:09:55,039 --> 00:09:57,080
Song Zhaoli has done so much for me.

159
00:09:57,519 --> 00:09:58,960
I want to be brave for him.

160
00:10:05,120 --> 00:10:06,320
Ji Xuan,

161
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,840
I allowed you into the group.

162
00:10:08,919 --> 00:10:11,480
I can also dismiss you.

163
00:10:13,639 --> 00:10:14,229
Chairman,

164
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,759
since I'm standing here
telling you this today,

165
00:10:17,039 --> 00:10:19,200
I'm ready to leave the company.

166
00:10:19,720 --> 00:10:20,519
But

167
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:23,759
Mr. Song is still
in charge of Song Group.

168
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:25,440
He has the right to know if I leave.

169
00:10:26,159 --> 00:10:26,919
I need to see him.

170
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:31,919
He's still unconscious right now.

171
00:10:32,320 --> 00:10:33,200
But

172
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,679
the person at his bedside

173
00:10:36,279 --> 00:10:37,559
is Xie Yao.

174
00:10:41,720 --> 00:10:42,320
Oh,

175
00:10:42,759 --> 00:10:44,080
one more thing.

176
00:10:44,519 --> 00:10:46,320
Their wedding date

177
00:10:46,519 --> 00:10:48,000
has been set.

178
00:10:48,679 --> 00:10:50,240
It's on the 1st

179
00:10:51,000 --> 00:10:52,159
of next month.

180
00:10:53,080 --> 00:10:54,399
That's your decision,

181
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:56,279
not Song Zhaoli's.

182
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:58,440
Goodbye, Chairman.

183
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,720
Still trying to outmaneuver me?

184
00:11:27,060 --> 00:11:28,852
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

185
00:11:29,012 --> 00:11:30,892
♪Flickering neon lights♪

186
00:11:31,092 --> 00:11:34,420
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

187
00:11:34,932 --> 00:11:37,204
♪Every star is♪

188
00:11:37,492 --> 00:11:41,364
♪My heartbeat for you♪

189
00:11:42,676 --> 00:11:44,500
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

190
00:11:44,660 --> 00:11:46,212
♪And land in your arms♪

191
00:11:46,612 --> 00:11:50,068
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

192
00:11:50,324 --> 00:11:52,884
♪In the blue sky♪

193
00:11:52,948 --> 00:11:57,076
♪Your smile still lingers♪

194
00:11:58,004 --> 00:12:01,652
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

195
00:12:01,908 --> 00:12:05,572
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

196
00:12:05,780 --> 00:12:08,692
♪Can't find a cure♪

197
00:12:08,692 --> 00:12:13,204
♪To love you after we've parted♪

198
00:12:13,396 --> 00:12:17,428
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

199
00:12:17,428 --> 00:12:21,292
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

200
00:12:21,292 --> 00:12:23,092
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

201
00:12:23,188 --> 00:12:28,340
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

202
00:12:28,980 --> 00:12:32,692
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

203
00:12:32,884 --> 00:12:35,636
♪Can't find a cure♪

204
00:12:35,764 --> 00:12:40,404
♪To love you after we've parted♪

205
00:12:40,572 --> 00:12:44,340
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

206
00:12:44,564 --> 00:12:48,148
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

207
00:12:48,372 --> 00:12:50,412
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

208
00:12:50,412 --> 00:12:55,412
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
